join 
Behavior: local 
Game: Operation Flashpoint (1.34) 
Description: Join all units in the array to given group.  
Maximum number of group members is: OFP: 12 Arma:&#160;? Arma2:&#160;? VBS2 
: "unlimited" (260+) 
To have a group member leave a group, join him with the grpNull group 
 (e.g. [guy1] join grpNull)  
Syntax:  
 unitArray join group 
Parameters: 
unitArray: Array 
group: Group or Object 
Return Value: 
 Nothing